# Design / UI hotspots

Full tables: `DESIGN_BRIEF.md` (open only if this rule is insufficient).

- Tokens only in `globals.css` (`:root` + `.dark`). No hex copies. No `dark:` sprawl. Don't re-palette dark.
- Elevation: `shadow-e1/e2/e3` only. Print classes must stay on elements.
- Progressive enhancement: GET filters/search; writes via server-action forms.
- Landing `queryPlans`: `perPage`/`sort` only (unfiltered). Brand from `src/lib/brand.ts`.
- Press feedback: `active:`; `hover:` dead on touch. Targets ≥44px.
